content: Easy to use and it's accurate and correct!
Super accurate predictions. If it could only predict a cloud coming over 13 secs before a transit after I drove 45 mins!

With the Calsky website no longer in operation this is the only way to get accurate predictions of ISS-Planetary transits. Thanks to this app I was able to find a shooting location and successfully get an excellent image of the ISS right next to Jupiter last week, a very rare occurrence. I will no doubt continue using it for the much more common Lunar and Solar transits.
Chasing the ISS can be frustrating, but success is always so rewarding. This app makes it all possible.
To the point. It does what it sets out to do, and offers a good range of customisation options. I looks forward to seeing my next transit!
La única en su tipo, muy precisa y acertada. Gran trabajo! / Hoy grabe mi primer transito de la ISS frente al Sol, no podría estar mas feliz :D
The software is easy to use and the prediction was spot on.
Worked perfectly. Captured the ISS passing straight over the moon.

I used this to plan my very first ISS solar transit and it worked perfectly, got some amazing shots.  It's very easy to use, and will find any transit within 100 miles and 11 days.  Author was very helpful and answered all my questions.  Pro version lets you save searches and locations, quite handy.
It works. Author very helpful. We got great images of ISS lunar transit thanks to this app. What else can I say?
